"title": "5694: generation",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5694: generation",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The population as a whole at any one time, or the interval of time separating parents and children.</p>\n<h2>All the contemporaries of an individual</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen7:1\">GEN 7:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod1:6\">EXO 1:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg2:10\">JDG 2:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps24:6\">PSA 24:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:8\">PSA 78:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps112:2\">PSA 112:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer2:31\">JER 2:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:29\">JER 7:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:16\">MAT 11:16</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:31\">LUK 7:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:32-Matt24:34\">MAT 24:32–24:34</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:28-Mark13:30\">MRK 13:28–13:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:29-Luke21:32\">LUK 21:29–21:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:40\">ACT 2:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:36\">ACT 13:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:14-Phil2:16\">PHP 2:14–2:16</a></p>\n<h2>The everlasting kingdom of God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam5:19\">LAM 5:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps72:5\">PSA 72:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:13\">PSA 145:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:3\">DAN 4:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:20-Eph3:21\">EPH 3:20–3:21</a></p>\n<h2>The passing of time expressed in terms of generations</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:15\">EXO 3:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen9:12\">GEN 9:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen17:12\">GEN 17:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:17\">EXO 12:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:5\">EXO 20:5</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:9\">DEU 5:9</a> <em>the enduring consequences of rebellion</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod31:16\">EXO 31:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev6:18\">LEV 6:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev23:41\">LEV 23:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num15:38\">NUM 15:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num35:29\">NUM 35:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut29:22\">DEU 29:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh22:27\">JOS 22:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth9:28\">EST 9:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps72:5\">PSA 72:5</a> <em>traditionally taken as referring to the Messiah</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps105:8\">PSA 105:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa34:10\">ISA 34:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer50:39\">JER 50:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:46-Luke1:50\">LUK 1:46–1:50</a></p>\n<h2>Past generations</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:9\">ISA 51:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:7\">DEU 32:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job8:8\">JOB 8:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:4\">ISA 41:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:4\">ISA 61:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:4-Eph3:5\">EPH 3:4–3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:25-Col1:26\">COL 1:25–1:26</a></p>\n<h2>The requirement to teach the next generation</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:9\">DEU 4:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:6-Deut6:7\">DEU 6:6–6:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:7\">DEU 32:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:30\">PSA 22:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps71:18\">PSA 71:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:1-Ps78:8\">PSA 78:1–78:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps79:13\">PSA 79:13</a></p>\n<h2>Time references by specific numbers of generations</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt1:17\">MAT 1:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:6-Exod34:7\">EXO 34:6–34:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:18\">NUM 14:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:9\">DEU 7:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut23:2-Deut23:3\">DEU 23:2–23:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut23:7-Deut23:8\">DEU 23:7–23:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs10:30\">2KI 10:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs15:12\">2KI 15:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:15\">1CH 16:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job42:16\">JOB 42:16</a></p>\n<h2>The generation that died in the wilderness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num32:13\">NUM 32:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut1:34-Deut1:36\">DEU 1:34–1:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut2:14\">DEU 2:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:5\">DEU 32:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:20\">DEU 32:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:7-Heb3:11\">HEB 3:7–3:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps95:7-Ps95:11\">PSA 95:7–95:11</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's comments concerning his own wicked generation</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:38\">MRK 8:38</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:39-Matt12:42\">MAT 12:39–12:42</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:29-Luke11:32\">LUK 11:29–11:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:43-Matt12:45\">MAT 12:43–12:45</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:4\">MAT 16:4</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:12\">MRK 8:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:17\">MAT 17:17</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:19\">MRK 9:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:41\">LUK 9:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:33-Matt23:36\">MAT 23:33–23:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:47-Luke11:51\">LUK 11:47–11:51</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:22-Luke17:25\">LUK 17:22–17:25</a></p>",
